## 15. Risks & Fallbacks

| Risk | Fallback |
|---|---|
| Laptop RAM pressure with 5 silos | 3 silos in dev/standard; 5 only for headline experiments |
| Kafka/Redpanda flakiness on Docker Desktop | file-based Structured Streaming source (drop-in `format("json")` on a watched dir); streaming semantics preserved |
| Delta Lake ↔ Spark version pinning pain | plain partitioned Parquet (config switch) |
| Mode B convergence instability on severe non-IID | raise `prox_mu`, lower `lr`, more rounds; Mode A as ground-truth cross-check |
| Kaggle download friction | mirror instructions + hash check; amplifier can also bootstrap from the ULB dataset |
| Dev-run wall time creep | keep dev config small; cache feature Parquet between rounds (features are round-invariant in batch mode) |

